jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132027855,imgsize-22500.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[D4vd murder case takes new turn as prosecutors reveal alleged motive before July court hearing and not guilty plea]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132022967.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The criminal case involving singer D4vd remains active in California. Prosecutors allege he killed 14-year-old Celeste Rivas Hernandez to stop her from exposing an alleged relationship, while the defense strongly denies those claims. Burke has pleaded not guilty, and the court will continue hearing the case, with a preliminary hearing scheduled for July 21, 2026.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/d4vd-murder-case-takes-new-turn-as-prosecutors-reveal-alleged-motive-before-july-court-hearing-and-not-guilty-plea/articleshow/132022967.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/d4vd-murder-case-takes-new-turn-as-prosecutors-reveal-alleged-motive-before-july-court-hearing-and-not-guilty-plea/articleshow/132022967.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-26T23:43:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132022937,imgsize-73519.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Clavicular’s controversial Paris visit takes stunning turn after viral kiss with Polish transgender model Adelaide Pali]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132038196.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Clavicular’s visit to Paris did not go as planned. His attempts to speak with women were mostly met with polite rejection, while many locals showed little interest in his online fame. After criticizing the experience, he later admitted he needs to improve his conversation skills. The trip has sparked wider discussion about internet popularity and real-life confidence.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/claviculars-controversial-paris-visit-takes-stunning-turn-after-viral-kiss-with-polish-transgender-model-adelaide-pali/articleshow/132038196.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/claviculars-controversial-paris-visit-takes-stunning-turn-after-viral-kiss-with-polish-transgender-model-adelaide-pali/articleshow/132038196.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-27T21:32:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Global Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132038179,imgsize-37637.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Charlie’s bloody coat was returned to Erika": Candace Owens releases unseen SUV photos after Charlie Kirk's assassination, raises new questions]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132026830.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens has released previously unseen photos from the SUV that transported Charlie Kirk to the hospital after he was fatally shot, claiming they raise new questions about the events following the attack. She pointed to shattered glass, a blood-stained bag, and Kirk's damaged microphone, while questioning how evidence was handled. Owens also highlighted alleged inconsistencies in witness accounts. However, her claims remain her interpretation and have not been officially verified by investigators.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/charlies-bloody-coat-was-returned-to-erika-candace-owens-releases-unseen-suv-photos-after-charlie-kirks-assassination-raises-new-questions/articleshow/132026830.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https:/