]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/an-anonymous-call-and-biden-cabinet-secretary-separated-from-his-4-year-old-twins-mix-of-rage-and-sadness/articleshow/132034765.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-27T17:56:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132034804,imgsize-199740.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Planning a trip to India? Here's why flight tickets from UAE are getting cheaper ]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132036291.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-india-airfares-drop-ahead-of-july-travel-rush-kerala-routes-see-sharpest-dip-report/articleshow/132036291.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-india-airfares-drop-ahead-of-july-travel-rush-kerala-routes-see-sharpest-dip-report/articleshow/132036291.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-27T19:41:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132036679,imgsize-180530.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hundreds of flights delayed at Heathrow and Gatwick as thunderstorms hit Southern England]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132034750.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Severe thunderstorms unleashed travel chaos across southern England, grounding hundreds of flights at Heathrow and Gatwick. Torrential rain, lightning, and hail forced air traffic control to implement safety restrictions, leading to significant delays and passengers facing long waits. While storms are expected to move on, airlines warn that flight schedules may take time to fully recover, impacting travellers throughout the day.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/hundreds-of-flights-delayed-at-heathrow-and-gatwick-as-thunderstorms-hit-southern-england/articleshow/132034750.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/hundreds-of-flights-delayed-at-heathrow-and-gatwick-as-thunderstorms-hit-southern-england/articleshow/132034750.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-27T17:52:47+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132034772,imgsize-550649.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Flying from UAE to India? Here's what you need to know as India brings back Air Suvidha portal]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132034604.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/flying-from-uae-to-india-heres-why-you-need-to-fill-air-suvidha-2-0-health-form-before-boarding/articleshow/132034604.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/flying-from-uae-to-india-heres-why-you-need-to-fill-air-suvidha-2-0-health-form-before-boarding/articleshow/132034604.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-27T17:49:48+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132034755,imgsize-96516.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[President Sheikh Mohamed orders Dh10 million relief package for Venezuela quake victims]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132033818.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Venezuela is reeling from devastating earthquakes, with rescue teams desperately searching for survivors. In a swift response, the United Arab Emirates has pledged Dh10 million in emergency humanitarian aid, directed by President His Highness Sheikh Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan. This significant contribution underscores the UAE's unwavering commitment to global humanitarian assistance during times of crisis, offering crucial support to the disaster-stricken nation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/president-sheikh-mohamed-orders-dh10-million-relief-package-for-venezuela-quake-victims/articleshow/132033818.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/president-sheikh-mohamed-orders-dh10-million-relief-package-for-venezuela-quake-victims/articleshow/132033818.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-27T17:12:33+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132033896,imgsize-79112.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UAE expands visa-on-arrival to 6 more countries, offering eligible travellers up to 60-day stay]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132033482.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Indian and Filipino passport holders can now enjoy easier entry into the UAE with an expanded visa-on-arrival program. Previously requiring visas from select Western nations, eligible travelers now benefit from this facility if they hold valid visas or residency from Australia, Canada, Japan, New Zealand, Singapore, or South Korea. This initiative aims to boost tourism and business ties, offering 14-day or 60-day stay options.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-expands-visa-on-arrival-to-6-more-countries-offering-eligible-travellers-up-to-60-day-stay/articleshow/1